list.name: Default
list.comment: Updated Angular JS. Added auto probing of new sources. Added extra probe info about the source when selecting it on the databaseadmin screen.

task.summary: Added JSON framework to all database objects

Added url separated from filename for sources. Added auto reconnect after error from select query due to database connection timeout. Added process manager for encode and probe services. Updated bootstrap to v4.1.1. Added process table to track various lone running processes.
Added more controls for process management. Added encoded progress table and support objects to keep track of encoding progress over time.
Updated libraries. Updated project pom to allow maven display updated check. Updated flyway to use new schema history table.
Added Full support for saving and loading JSON Objects from the database. Generalised probe function. Probe is run on all new sources automatically.
